enum CoordinateOnItemObject::state_t [private]
 

The possible states of this object.

Enumeration values:
ADDING_ITEMS  Initial state where items can be added.
SENDING_COORDINATE_REQUEST  Sending position packets.
AWAITING_COORDINATE_REPLY  Awaiting position reply packets.
DONE  Finnished successfully.
ERROR  Some error has accured, don't use any result data.
